.bs-callout.bs-callout-primary
  %p
    These bars show the current resource usage in your project. The total
    length of each bar indicates the quota that you have been granted by your
    domain administrator.
  %p
    If you need more resources, you can request a larger quota from your domain administrator.
  - if @warning
    %p.text-danger
      %strong Note:
      Some of your current quotas exceed your approved quota. The approved quota will
      appear as an extra mark on the bar to the left. For this case an
      automatic alert is issued to your domain administrator.
